==Description==
The '''Hard Stone''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Hard Stone''' has a value of 4 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Hard Stone appears in the Underground as a 2x2 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:HardStoneMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Max Revives can be found in the [[Underground]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Graveler.png|30px]] Graveler, [[File:Golem.png|30px]] Golem, [[File:Onix.png|30px]] Onix, [[File:Corsola.png|30px]] Corsola, [[File:Nosepass.png|30px]] Nosepass, [[File:Aron.png|30px]] Aron, [[File:Lairon.png|30px]] Lairon, [[File:Aggron.png|30px]] Aggron, and [[File:Probopass.png|30px]] Probopass, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

